def addlabels(x,y,z,horiz=False,rot=75):
    if horiz==True:
        for i in range(len(x)):
            plt.text(y[i],i-0.15,z[i],rotation=rot)
    else:
        for i in range(len(x)):
            plt.text(i-0.15,y[i],z[i],rotation=rot)

def classify_data(df,excl_cat=''):
    cat_dict ={}
    for col in df.columns:
        if col!=excl_cat:
            if df[col].isin([0,1]).all() or df[col].dtype=='bool':
                cat_dict[col]='cat'
            elif df[col].dtype=='object':
                cat_dict[col]='obj'
            else:
                cat_dict[col]='num'
    return cat_dict

def plot_df(df,n_cols,w,h,by_cat, idcol):
    colons = []
    for i in pd.Series(df.columns).index:
        if df.columns[i] != idcol:
            colons.append(i)
    df=df.iloc[:,colons]
    col_cat=classify_data(df,by_cat)
    #      
    cat_att=[]
    num_att=[]
    obj_att=[]
    
    for i in col_cat:
        if (col_cat[i] == 'cat') & (col_cat[i] != by_cat):
            cat_att.append(i)
        elif (col_cat[i] == 'num') & (col_cat[i] != by_cat):
            num_att.append(i)
        elif (col_cat[i] == 'obj') & (col_cat[i] != by_cat):
            obj_att.append(i)
    cat_no = len(cat_att)
    num_no=len(num_att)*2
    obj_no=len(obj_att)
    tot_no = cat_no+num_no+obj_no
    rows_cat = cat_no//n_cols
    if cat_no % n_cols !=0:
        rows_cat += 1
    tot_no+=cat_no % n_cols
    rows_num = num_no//n_cols
    if num_no % n_cols !=0:
        rows_num += 1
    rows_tot = rows_cat + rows_num
    if cat_no % 2 !=0:
        num_st_pos = cat_no + 1
    else:
        num_st_pos = cat_no
    position = range(1,tot_no+1)

    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(w,h*rows_tot))
    fig.tight_layout()
    f = 0
    a = 0
    x = 0
    for i in range(len(cat_att)+len(num_att)+len(obj_att)):
        if i - len(cat_att) < 0:
            for x in (0,1):
                ax = fig.add_subplot(rows_tot,n_cols,position[i+a])
                sns.barplot(y=cat_att[i],x=by_cat, data=df[[by_cat, cat_att[i]]])
                ax.set_title(col_names[cat_att[i]] + ', ' + col_names[by_cat])
                ax.set_ylabel(col_names[cat_att[i]])
                ax.set_xticks(df[cat_att[i]].unique())
                ax.set_xticklabels(df[cat_att[i]].unique())
                ax.set_xlabel('')
        elif i - len(cat_att)-len(num_att) < 0:
            z = num_st_pos + i-len(cat_att) + f
            ax = fig.add_subplot(rows_tot,n_cols,position[z])
            sns.histplot(x=df[num_att[i-cat_no]],hue = df[by_cat],common_norm=False)
            sns.kdeplot(x=df[num_att[i-cat_no]],hue = df[by_cat],common_norm=False)
            ax.set_title(col_names[num_att[i-cat_no]])
            ax.set_xlabel('')
            ax.set_ylabel('-')
            #ax.ticklabel_format(style='plain', axis='x')
            plt.xticks(rotation=70)
            f +=1
            z = num_st_pos + i-len(cat_att) + f
            ax = fig.add_subplot(rows_tot,n_cols,position[z])
            sns.boxplot(x=df[num_att[i-cat_no]],hue=df[by_cat])
            ax.set_title(col_names[num_att[i-cat_no]])
            ax.set_xlabel('')
            #ax.ticklabel_format(style='plain', axis='x')
            plt.xticks(rotation=70)            
    plt.show()

def top(what,by, df_set,number,name,kind = 'bar',size=(15,15)):
    i=0
    if kind=='bar':
        for frame in df_set:
            df_user=frame.groupby(what)[by].sum().sort_values(ascending=False).to_frame().reset_index()
            top_number=df_user[what].head(number)
            df_user['share']=(df_user[by]/df_user[by].sum()).round(3)
            df_user=df_user.sort_values(by='share', ascending=True).reset_index(drop=True)
            #display(df_user)
            plt.figure(figsize=size)
            df_user.plot(kind='barh', x=what,y=by)
            addlabels(df_user[what], df_user[by],df_user['share'],True)
            plt.xticks(rotation=45, fontsize=15)
            plt.yticks(fontsize=15)
            plt.title(name[i],fontsize=20)
            plt.ylabel(what, fontsize=17)
            plt.show()
            i+=1
    elif kind=='pie':
        for frame in df_set:
            df_user=frame.groupby(what)[by].sum().sort_values(ascending=False).to_frame().reset_index()
            df_user2=df_user.head(5)
            df_user=df_user[~df_user[what].isin(df_user2[what])]
            df_user2.loc[5,what]='other'
            df_user2.loc[5,by]=df_user[by].sum()
            plt.figure()
            df_user2.plot(kind='pie',labels=df_user2[what],y=by,autopct='%1.1f%%', figsize=size, fontsize=15)
            plt.legend(fontsize=12)
            plt.title(name[i],fontsize=20)
            plt.ylabel(by,fontsize=18)
            plt.show()
            i+=1

def b_g_r(s):
    cm=sns.color_palette("RdYlGn_r", as_cmap=True)
    max_val = max(s.max(), abs(s.min()))
    norm = colors.Normalize(0,max_val)
    normed = norm(abs(s.values))
    c = [colors.rgb2hex(x) for x in plt.cm.get_cmap(cm)(normed)]
    return ['background-color: %s' % color for color in c]

def b_g(s):
    cm=sns.color_palette("RdYlGn", as_cmap=True)
    max_val = max(s.max(), abs(s.min()))
    norm = colors.Normalize(0,max_val)
    normed = norm(abs(s.values))
    c = [colors.rgb2hex(x) for x in plt.cm.get_cmap(cm)(normed)]
    return ['background-color: %s' % color for color in c]

for col in df.columns:
    if not col in ['churn','userid']:
        if data_class[col] == 'num':
            z = np.abs(st.zscore(df[col],nan_policy='omit'))
            threshold = 3
            df_outliers = df[z>threshold]
            df_loc=df.drop(df_outliers.index)
            plt.figure(figsize=(10,5))
            sns.histplot(x=col,hue='churn',data=df_loc,common_norm=False, 
                         stat='density',
                         multiple='dodge',
                         kde=True)
            plt.title(col_names[col],fontsize=16)
            plt.xlabel('')
            plt.ylabel(' ', fontsize=12)
        elif data_class[col]=='cat':
            plt.figure()
            sns.barplot(y=col,x='churn',data=df)
            plt.title(col_names[col],fontsize=16)
            plt.xlabel('',fontsize=14)
            plt.ylabel('', fontsize=12)
        elif data_class[col]=='dis':
            plt.figure()
            sns.barplot(y=col,x='churn',data=df)

            plt.xlabel('',fontsize=14)

for col in columns_study:
        if col not in ['userid','age','churn','city','gender']:
            plt.figure(figsize=(14,5))
            if col=='balance':
                z = np.abs(st.zscore(df[col],nan_policy='omit'))
                threshold = 3
                df_outliers = df[z>threshold]
                df_loc=df.drop(df_outliers.index)
            else:
                df_loc=df
            data_seg = df_loc.loc[(df_loc['age']>=18)&(df_loc['age']<40) & (df_loc['products'] >3)]
            sns.histplot(data=data_seg,x=col,hue='churn',stat='density',multiple='dodge')
            plt.ticklabel_format(style='plain')
            if data_class[col]=='cat':
                plt.xticks([0,1])
            elif data_class[col]=='num':
                plt.xticks(pd.Series(data_seg[col].quantile([0,0.25,0.5,0.6,0.75,0.95,1]).reset_index()[col].unique()),
                           rotation=45)
            elif col=='products':
                plt.xticks(data_seg['products'].unique())
            plt.xlabel(col_names[col])
            plt.ylabel(' ')
        plt.show()
